question: return me the total citations of papers in the VLDB conference before 2005 .
qdmr: return papers ;return #1 in the  VLDB conference ;return #2 before 2005 ;return citations of #3 ;return number of  #4 for each  #3 ;return sum #4
sql_gold: select sum ( publication_0.citation_num ) from conference as conference_0, publication as publication_0 where conference_0.name = "VLDB" and publication_0.year < 2005 and conference_0.cid = publication_0.cid
sql_ground: SELECT SUM(publication.citation_num) FROM publication, conference WHERE publication.cid = conference.cid AND publication.pid IN ( SELECT publication.pid FROM publication, conference WHERE publication.cid = conference.cid AND conference.name = 'VLDB' AND publication.year < 2005 )

question: return me the total citations of papers in the VLDB conference in each year .
qdmr: return papers ;return #1 in the  VLDB conference ;return citations of #2 ;return number of  #3 for each year
sql_gold: select publication_0.year, sum ( publication_0.citation_num ) from conference as conference_0, publication as publication_0 where conference_0.name = "VLDB" and conference_0.cid = publication_0.cid group by publication_0.year
sql_ground: SELECT publication.year, SUM(publication.citation_num) FROM publication, conference WHERE publication.cid = conference.cid AND publication.pid IN ( SELECT publication.pid FROM publication, conference WHERE publication.cid = conference.cid AND conference.name = 'VLDB' ) GROUP BY publication.year

question: return me the number of papers published in the VLDB conference in each year .
qdmr: return papers ;return #1 that  are published in the  VLDB conference ;return number of  #2 for each year
sql_gold: select publication_0.year, count ( distinct ( publication_0.title ) ) from conference as conference_0, publication as publication_0 where conference_0.name = "VLDB" and conference_0.cid = publication_0.cid group by publication_0.year
sql_ground: SELECT publication.year, COUNT(DISTINCT publication.title) FROM publication, conference WHERE publication.cid = conference.cid AND conference.name = 'VLDB' GROUP BY publication.year

sql_gold: select publication_0.title from author as author_0, publication as publication_0, writes as writes_0 where author_0.name = "H. V. Jagadish" and author_0.aid = writes_0.aid and publication_0.pid = writes_0.pid

question: return me the paper in PVLDB with more than 200 citations .

question: return me the paper after 2000 in Databases area with more than 200 citations .
qdmr: return paper ;return #1 after 2000 ;return #2 in Databases area ;return citations of  #3 ;return number of  #4 for each  #3 ;return #3 where  #5 is more than  200
sql_gold: select publication_0.title from domain as domain_0, domain_publication as domain_publication_0, publication as publication_0 where domain_0.name = "Databases" and publication_0.citation_num  >  200 and publication_0.year  >  2000 and domain_0.did = domain_publication_0.did and domain_publication_0.pid = publication_0.pid
sql_ground: SELECT publication.title FROM publication, domain_publication, domain WHERE publication.pid = domain_publication.pid AND domain_publication.did = domain.did AND publication.title IN ( SELECT publication.title FROM publication, domain_publication, domain WHERE publication.pid = domain_publication.pid AND domain_publication.did = domain.did AND publication.citation_num > 200 AND publication.year > 2000 AND domain.name = 'Databases' ) AND publication.citation_num > 200 AND publication.year > 2000 AND domain.name = 'Databases'

question: return me the paper after 2000 in PVLDB with more than 200 citations .
qdmr: return papers ;return #1 in  PVLDB ;return #2 that are after 2000 ;return citations of #3 ;return number of  #4 for each #3 ;return #3 where #5 is more than 200
sql_gold: select publication_0.title from journal as journal_0, publication as publication_0 where journal_0.name = "PVLDB" and publication_0.citation_num  >  200 and publication_0.year  >  2000 and journal_0.jid = publication_0.jid
sql_ground: SELECT publication.title FROM publication, journal WHERE publication.jid = journal.jid AND publication.title IN ( SELECT publication.title FROM publication, journal WHERE publication.jid = journal.jid AND journal.name = 'PVLDB' AND publication.citation_num > 200 AND publication.year > 2000 ) AND journal.name = 'PVLDB' AND publication.citation_num > 200 AND publication.year > 2000 GROUP BY publication.title HAVING COUNT(publication.citation_num) > 200
